* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1855|ja|1855|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The event of the {{Ansei Edo Earthquake}} is recorded, with heavy damage concentrated in downtown areas and over 7,000 fatalities. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government standardized military methods: the army adopted French models, and the navy British ones.
== Births == * {{ill|Baireki|ja|Hōreki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1758|ja|1758|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ryōkan|ja|良寛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, calligrapher († {{ill|1831|ja|1831|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|775|ja|775|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kibi Shinbi|ja|吉備真備|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a sinologist and court official (* {{ill|693|ja|693|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 22nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1553|ja|1553|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamazaki Sōkan|ja|山崎宗鑑|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|ja|1465|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1643|ja|1643|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tenkai|ja|天海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|ja|1536|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
