* {{ill|Gekkyō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|110|ja|110|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=draft|12=draft}}  departed to subdue the eastern barbarians.
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The event of the {{Ansei Edo Earthquake}}  is recorded, with heavy damage concentrated in downtown areas and over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government standardized military methods: the army adopted French models, and the navy British ones.
== Births ==
