* {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft}} 22nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1553|ja|1553|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamazaki Sōkan|ja|山崎宗鑑|12=draft|12=draft}} , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|ja|1465|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
