'''October 20''' is the 20th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Gekkyō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|qq=|12=draft}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|110|ja|110|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|12=draft}}  departed to subdue the eastern barbarians.
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The event of the {{Ansei Edo Earthquake|qq=}}  is recorded, with heavy damage concentrated in downtown areas and over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government standardized military methods: the army adopted French models, and the navy British ones.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Baireki|ja|Hōreki|qq=|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ryōkan|ja|良寛|qq=|12=draft}} , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, calligrapher († {{ill|1831|ja|1831|qq=|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|775|ja|775|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kibi Shinbi|ja|吉備真備|qq=|12=draft}} , a sinologist and court official (* {{ill|693|ja|693|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|qq=|12=draft}} 22nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1553|ja|1553|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamazaki Sōkan|ja|山崎宗鑑|qq=|12=draft}} , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|ja|1465|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1643|ja|1643|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tenkai|ja|天海|qq=|12=draft}} , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|ja|1536|qq=|12=draft}} ).

