{{Not to be confused with|October 20|qq=October 20}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月二十|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 20일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 20''' is the 20th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} .
== Events == * [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Gekkyō Tennō]] 40th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:110|110]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル}} departed to subdue the eastern barbarians. * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 11|November 11]] ） – The event of the {{Ansei Edo Earthquake|qq=}} is recorded, with heavy damage concentrated in downtown areas and over 7,000 fatalities. * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1870|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 26|October 26]] ） – The Meiji government standardized military methods: the army adopted French models, and the navy British ones. == Births == * [[:en:Hōreki|Hōreki]] 8th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1758|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ） – [[:en:Ryōkan|Ryōkan]] , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, calligrapher († {{ill|1831|ja|1831|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1831|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Hōki|Hōki]] 6th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|775|ja|775|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/775|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 700}} [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ） – [[:en:Kibi no Makibi|Kibi Shinbi]] , a sinologist and court official (* [[:en:693|693]] ). * {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun (era)|qq=}} 22nd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1553|1553]] [[:en:November 7|November 7]] ） – [[:en:Yamazaki Sōkan|Yamazaki Sōkan]] , a renka master and haiku poet (* [[:en:1465|1465]] ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 20th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1643|ja|1643|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1643|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1600}} [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ） – [[:en:Tenkai|Tenkai]] , a Tendai monk (* [[:en:1536|1536]] ).
